rComments: The best professor in my first year!! He is so caring and I would definitely take his class again despite the amount of assigned readings. However, I actually learned a a lot from the assigned readings and it was totally worth it to spend the time on them.

He is by far one of the best profs in the German Department and by far the best one when it comes to teaching language courses. He is always enthusiastic and encourages students to participate and engage themselves in class. Although not everybody may get his humour I would recommend his classes to anybody. Great learning experience!
